Central Air Southwest quick facts

Type: carrierRegion: North AmericaCountry: United StatesBase airport: Charles B. Wheeler Downtown AirportYear established: 1974

Airline Overview and Services

Central Air Southwest is a currently operating North American cargo airline with its base at Charles B. Wheeler Downtown Airport, in Kansas City, United States.

This airline's and its ICAO code is CTL. Founded 50 years ago in 1974, the airline is one of the oldest airline companies in the world.
